  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK770">
<l>nilaimakkaḷ cāla vuṭaitteṉiṉun tāṉai</l>
<l>talaimakka ḷilvaḻi yil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though an army may contain a large number of permanent soldiers, it cannot last if it has no generals.</l>
            </lg>
